-- China CNOOC says Nexen deal to up production by 20 percent
-- 
-- Mon Jul 23, 2012 8:23am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/23/us-cnooc-nexen-production-idUSBRE86M0J820120723

 

 BEIJING  (Reuters) - China's top offshore oil producer CNOOC Ltd said its planned $15.1 billion deal to buy Canada's Nexen Inc could raise its production by 20 percent, and its proved oil and gas reserves by 30 percent. 
 (Reporting by Wan Xu and Koh Gui Qing; Editing by Jon Loades-Carter)